                            <h4>ISLAMABAD</h4>
                            <p>Pakistan's capital, Islamabad, is one of the most attractive cities in the South Asian region. The city's different sectors and zones are adorned with wide, tree-lined streets,
                                making it both accessible and spectacular.
                                The city combines a rich history, a crossroads of civilizations, and a pleasant climate. </p>

