                        <div class="portfolio-info">
                            <h4>MULTAN</h4>
                            <p>Multan is famous for local cuisines especially Sohan Halwa. Multan is known as Southeast Asia's oldest civilization. Multan today is a blend of old and new Pakistani culture. In the Old Town, there is a lot of rush and bustle, but in the New City, there is the comfort of a five-star hotels and quiet streets.
                                The Old City boasts a fascinating Bazaar, Food as well as many ornately constructed Sufi shrines.</p>

                        </div>
                    </div>
